  "text": "For preparation of tissue homogenates, frozen heart samples from left ventricle were crushed at liquid N 2 temperature and then homogenized to measure the phosphorylation and protein levels of contractile machinery complex as described previously [CITATION_1] (CaMKII, phospho-CaMKII-Thr286, PKA, phospho-PKAThr198, FKBP12.6, RyR2, phospho-RyR2-Ser 2808 , phospho-NF B, NF B, and -actin were identified using specific antibodies with recommended dilutions of either Santa Cruz biotechnology (USA) or Badrilla Ltd. (UK) companies). Density analysis of protein bands was performed using ImageJ programme.",
